    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring a double-VANOS system that provides exceptional torque throughout the power band. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. To ensure structural longevity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, addressing the platform's primary stress point. Suspension dynamics are maintained by a refreshed multi-link setup, offering the tactile feedback and lateral grip expected of the M-division. While the exterior displays a light patina, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response are impeccably sharp, making this a turn-key performance machine for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
